title: NFL Week 9 Picks Against the Spread
description: The Jets look to prove themselves against the Bills, the Dolphins and Bears will show off trade pickups, and Derrick Henry and the Titans face well rested Kansas City.
dc:creator: David Hill
media:description: Josh Allen, left, and Stefon Diggs have led the Bills to a 6-1 record, including wins over the former M.V.P.s Lamar Jackson, Patrick Mahomes and Aaron Rodgers.
